-- WestLB's Request on Sale of WestImmo Retail Unit Is Sent to European Union
-- B y   R a i n e r   B u e r g i n
-- 2010-10-29T10:12:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-29/westlb-s-request-on-sale-of-westimmo-retail-unit-is-sent-to-european-union.html
The German government has forwarded
WestLB AG’s request for an extension of the deadline to sell
Westdeutsche ImmobilienBank AG to the European Commission,
German government spokesman Christoph Steegmans told reporters
in Berlin today.  The request “is with the commission, we’ll get an
answer,” Steegmans told reporters.  The current stipulation is that WestImmo be sold by Dec.
31, 2010.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rainer Buergin at 
 rbuergin1@bloomberg.net  